      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GAME OF PHONES (5) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Dim Sim Rixi (22.88) in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Can find winning form. GRAFFITI (3) hit the ground running from out wide and was on speed early but swamped late when 6th at Bendigo in a Grade 5. Has a good record here at this journey. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from five starts. Key player if finds best. SUGAR SHINE (7) wasn't far away at the finish when 4th and beaten only 4.5 lengths (23.08) at this track. The form from his last run stacks up well. Key runner on best form. OUR BOY BILLY (1) can return to form after missing the top-three at this circuit last time out.",
